data.description: Welcome to Bridge Hollow Estates a well established private gated community of 20 acre plus lots / Ranchettes. This beautiful French Farm Style House is reminiscent of being in Provence and is nestled on a rambling secluded 21.46 acres. Panoramic views from every room of dramatic mountain vistas. Wild life like Moose, Elk, Deer, Rabbits and many kinds of birds are some of the regular guests on the land. This is a great ''Lock and Leave'' house or a full time year round access property. Awesome things about this home: Pellet Stove, Dog Wash, Super Mud Room, Attached Garage, Huge Outdoor Patio, Snow removal to the driveway, Hardwood and Slate Floors, High Ceilings and Main Floor Master. Wanship is approximately 15 minutes to Kimball Junction,  25 minutes to Park City, 40 minutes to Salt Lake City and 50 minutes to Salt Lake International Airport.
